      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/812174-the-sicilian">Quotes from The Sicilian</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
